---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Takedown Requests" description="How to request removal of content from Golden Path.">
  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <h1>Takedown &amp; IP Complaints</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>We respect intellectual property. If you own rights in material shown here — box art, an embedded video, or text — and want it removed, please contact us.</p>

    <h2>How to submit a request</h2>
    <p>Email <a href="mailto:eevee.bork@icloud.com">eevee.bork@icloud.com</a> with:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>The specific URL where the material appears</li>
      <li>A description of the material and your rights in it</li>
      <li>Proof you hold the relevant rights</li>
      <li>Your contact details</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Response time</h2>
    <p>We aim to respond within 5 working days and will remove or correct promptly where the claim is valid.</p>

    <h2>Other channels</h2>
    <p>Cloudflare and YouTube also have their own notice-and-takedown processes for content served through their platforms.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
